  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Instalao de Sound Theme Freedesktop</title>

    <para>
      Install <application>Sound Theme Freedesktop</application> by running the
following commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Esse pacote no vem com uma sute de teste.
    </para>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usurio(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

